simulator.elevatorcontrol

Class Utility

  • java.lang.Object
    • simulator.elevatorcontrol.Utility

  • public class Utility
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides some example utility classes that might be useful in more than one spot. It is okay to create new classes (or modify the ones given below), but you may not use utility classes in such a way that they constitute a communication channel between controllers.
